so-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>‰”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; LETTER-SPACING: -1pt\">注<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>，死亡率还应加上出生率，则死亡率超过</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>205.8</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>‰。宣城县这几年死亡的人中，大多为非正常死亡。非正常死亡的绝大部分是因饥饿而死，或因饥饿引发的各种疾病而死。据安徽省公安厅</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1979</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年编印的《安徽省人口统计资料（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1949</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>—</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1978</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>）》记载，宣城县</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1950</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年至</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1953</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年人口死亡率分别为</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>7.12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>‰、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>7.01</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>‰、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>7.13</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>‰、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>9.60</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>‰。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; LETTER-SPACING: -1pt\">注<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>公开出版的省公安厅提供的人口统计资料，则记载宣城县</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1954</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1957</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1962</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年的死亡率分别为</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>18.78</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>‰、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>10.92</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>‰、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>10.27</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>‰。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; LETTER-SPACING: -1pt\">注<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>据《宣城县志》记载，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1959</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年和</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1960</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年虽有些小旱、小涝，但基本上属于正常年景。正常人口死亡率如以灾前的</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1957</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年计算，则</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>1959</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><FONT size=3>年至</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 f